# UiType & field-type system

## Two distinct type resolutions — never conflate them

| Method | Owner | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `Field::getUiTypeName(): string` | `src/Modules/Base/Models/Field.php` | Semantic type for business logic: import, workflow, reports, query conditions. Uses `SEMANTIC_TYPE_MAP`. |
| `Field::getFieldDataType()` | same — alias for `getUiTypeName()` | Kept for backward compatibility. **No return-type annotation** (see pitfall below). |
| `WebserviceField::getFieldDataType()` | `src/Webservices/WebserviceField.php` | REST API type from `vtiger_ws_fieldtype` + `typeofdata` fallback. `V~O` → `'string'` is correct for the API but **wrong for UI**. Never use as a UI fallback. |
| `BaseUiType::getInstanceFromField()` | `src/Modules/Base/UiTypes/BaseUiType.php` | Picks the renderer class via `UITYPE_CLASS_MAP` (uitype int → class suffix). **Does not call `getFieldDataType()`** for known uitypes — fully independent of the webservice layer. |

---

## UITYPE_CLASS_MAP — renderer selection (BaseUiType)

Located at `BaseUiType::UITYPE_CLASS_MAP`. Maps uitype integer directly to the UiType class name suffix used for rendering.

| uitype | Class suffix | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| 3, 4 | `RecordNumber` | |
| 8 | `TotalTime` | |
| 9 | `Percentage` | |
| 10, 26, 50–51, 57–59, 73, 75–76, 80–81, 101, 357 | `Reference` | All reference variants |
| 11 | `Phone` | |
| 13 | `Email` | |
| 15, 33 | `Picklist` | uitype 33 = multipicklist stored as single value |
| 16 | `Multipicklist` | |
| 17 | `Url` | |
| 19–21, 24, 300 | `Text` | Multi-line text variants |
| 28 | `DocumentsFileUpload` | |
| 30, 342 | `Recurrence` | |
| 32 | `Languages` | |
| 52 | `UserCreator` | |
| 53 | `Owner` | |
| 54 | `Multiowner` | |
| 55 | `Salutation` / `StringType` | Disambiguated by field name: `salutationtype` → `Salutation`, anything else → `StringType` |
| 56, 156 | `Boolean` | |
| 61, 69 | `Image` | |
| 66 | `ReferenceProcess` | |
| 67 | `ReferenceLink` | |
| 68 | `ReferenceSubProcess` | |
| 71, 72 | `Currency` | |
| 85 | `StringType` | Skype field — no dedicated class |
| 98 | `UserRole` | |
| 117 | `CurrencyList` | |
| 120 | `SharedOwner` | |
| 301 | `Modules` | |
| 302 | `Tree` | `getAllValue()` for advanced-search picklists in `Field::getFieldInfo()` |
| 303 | `Taxes` | |
| 304 | `InventoryLimit` | |
| 305 | `MultiReferenceValue` | |
| 306 | `MultiReference` | Manual multi-record reference; comma-separated CRM IDs in TEXT |
| 308 | `RangeTime` | |
| 309 | `CategoryMultipicklist` | Same picklist path as Tree — `getAllValue()` delegates to `Tree` |
| 310 | `CompanySelect` | |
| 311 | `MultiImage` | |
| 330 | `MultiAttachmentJson` | JSON multi-attachment (e.g. Candidates `cv_img_file`); not AJAX-editable |
| 358 | `MailSmtpSelect` | |
| *(unmapped)* | derived from `getFieldDataType()` | Fallback for custom/future uitypes |

Resolution order inside `getInstanceFromField()`:
1. `\App\Modules\{Module}\UiTypes\{Suffix}` — module-specific override
2. `\App\Modules\Base\UiTypes\{Suffix}` — base implementation
3. `BaseUiType` — generic fallback (renders `String.tpl`)

